-- Argentine stocks rises on optimism about debt talks - traders
-- By Jorge Otaola
-- Tue Jul 29, 2014 04:03PM EDT
-- None



BUENOS AIRES, July 29 (Reuters) - Argentina's MerVal stock index <.MERV> reversed losses and rose 5.1 pct on Tuesday on increased optimism about last-minute debt talks in New York aimed at avoiding an Argentine default, traders said.

